1. Deploy contracts on testnet.


2. Connect frontend & backend.


3. Test fusion flow end-to-end.


4. Iterate, secure, and audit contracts.


5. Deploy mainnet after audit.


6. Release web + mobile apps.


7. Monetize via MOG token fees and NFT rare card drops.




